#### REQUIREMENTS 

    Software required on RHEL/CentOS: 
        yum install php-cli php-mysql perl-Time-HiRes

    Software required on Ubuntu/Debian: 
        apt-get install php5-cli php5-mysqlnd 
        mailutils can also be required.

Have a nice day!
